h-l%C6%B0u-%E1%BA%A9m/poem-2qnkAWA6LbVhBqFNuGNIKQ">Tây giang nguyệt - Ẩm Sơn đình lưu ẩm - 西江月－飲山亭留飲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Nh%C3%A2n/author-KBIyiFFEwjDCBu_ejCqDtg">Lưu Nhân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng/T%C3%A2y-H%E1%BB%93-ca/poem-A0_rIAtO11uVAlXpUBjyrA">Tây Hồ ca - 西湖歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Ho%E1%BA%B1ng/author-FIjl4n7erAHsrrDCeeDftA">Vương Ngạn Hoằng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/V%C4%83n-Th%C3%B9-ch%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-xdr3NQsVIPcEDHKmgwiQVA">Văn Thù chương - 文殊章</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/author-RGxtMe1sV6AuAbjteu9Sdg">Jingak Hyesim</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam-th%E1%BA%BF-ch%C3%AD-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-pwYVzZ3mpuX7PHg6BRMRqA">Việt Nam thế chí tự - 越南世志序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-T%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%91c/author-AQI-nV6p-JhBHd--0I9cWA">Hồ Tông Thốc</a>)<br></div>	</div>
